## Key Changes:

1. **New Container**: Added `.header-right-group` div that wraps both the date range and filter button
2. **Flexbox Layout**: The group uses flexbox to keep items aligned horizontally
3. **Gap**: 12px gap between date range and filter button (8px on smaller screens)
4. **Alignment**: Everything stays aligned to the right side of the header
5. **Title on Left**: History title stays on the left with its gradient bar
6. **Responsive**: Both elements scale down together on smaller screens

